claim.claim-text:
24. A test structure comprising: 
a first plurality of conductive lines; 
a second plurality of conductive lines orthogonal to the second conductive lines, wherein the first conductive lines are on a different level than the second conductive lines; 
a plurality of self-aligned contacts designed to be coupled to the first plurality of conductive lines and not the second plurality of conductive lines, wherein the test structure forms part of a product wafer and is designed to mimic an array structure having self-aligned contacts.
